HEADWORD: Pesterment
<hw>Pes"ter*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
pestering, or the state of being pestered; vexation; worry.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧The trouble and <xex>pesterment</xex> of children.⟦rdquo⟧
